OL,14,     Fspine, pelvis and leg injuries
OL,15,     Fthat require high-risk surgery
OL,16,     Fusing bone hooks. And a plasterer
OL,17,     Fis put in a coma after a head-on
OL,18,     Ftraffic collision.
